sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client (React SPA)
    participant AC as AuthController
    participant AS as AuthService
    participant UR as UserRepository
    participant JWT as JwtService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over C,DB: === LOGIN FLOW ===

    C->>AC: POST /api/v1/auth/login {email, password}
    AC->>AS: login(email, password)
    AS->>UR: findByEmail(email)
    UR->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>UR: User record
    UR-->>AS: User entity

    alt User not found
        AS-->>AC: throw UnauthorizedException
        AC-->>C: 401 {error: "Invalid credentials"}
    end

    AS->>AS: bcrypt.compare(password, user.password_hash)

    alt Password mismatch
        AS-->>AC: throw UnauthorizedException
        AC-->>C: 401 {error: "Invalid credentials"}
    end

    AS->>JWT: sign({sub: user.id, roles}, {expiresIn: '15m'})
    JWT-->>AS: accessToken
    AS->>JWT: sign({sub: user.id, jti: uuid}, {expiresIn: '7d'})
    JWT-->>AS: refreshToken
    AS->>DB: UPDATE users SET last_login_at = NOW()
    AS->>DB: INSERT INTO refresh_tokens (user_id, token_hash)
    AS-->>AC: {accessToken, refreshToken, user}
    AC-->>C: 200 {accessToken, user} + Set-Cookie: refreshToken (HttpOnly, Secure)

    Note over C,DB: === PROTECTED REQUEST FLOW ===

    C->>AC: GET /api/v1/projects (Authorization: Bearer <token>)
    AC->>AC: JwtAuthGuard intercepts

    alt Token expired or invalid
        AC-->>C: 401 {error: "Unauthorized"}
    end

    AC->>JWT: verify(token)
    JWT-->>AC: payload {sub, roles}
    AC->>UR: findById(payload.sub)
    UR-->>AC: User entity
    AC->>AC: RolesGuard: check user.roles >= required
    AC->>AC: PermissionsGuard: check specific permissions

    alt Insufficient permissions
        AC-->>C: 403 {error: "Forbidden"}
    end

    AC->>AC: Execute route handler
    AC-->>C: 200 {data: [...projects]}

    Note over C,DB: === TOKEN REFRESH FLOW ===

    C->>AC: POST /api/v1/auth/refresh (Cookie: refreshToken)
    AC->>AS: refreshTokens(refreshToken)
    AS->>JWT: verify(refreshToken)
    AS->>DB: SELECT * FROM refresh_tokens WHERE token_hash = ?

    alt Token revoked or invalid
        AS-->>AC: throw UnauthorizedException
        AC-->>C: 401 {error: "Invalid refresh token"}
    end

    AS->>DB: DELETE FROM refresh_tokens WHERE id = ? (rotate)
    AS->>JWT: sign(newAccessPayload)
    AS->>JWT: sign(newRefreshPayload)
    AS->>DB: INSERT INTO refresh_tokens (new token hash)
    AS-->>AC: {accessToken, refreshToken}
    AC-->>C: 200 {accessToken} + Set-Cookie: new refreshToken
